# Checkwright core-file manifest — gate-sdk/SPEC.md §check-core-files.
# One repo-relative path per line (`#` comments, blank lines ignored). The gate
# is red when a listed path is missing from the worktree or untracked. Retiring
# a surface deliberately means deleting its line in the same commit that removes
# the file — that manifest edit is the diff-visible intentional-removal valve.

# Iteration state machine + governance charter.
TASK-QUEUE.md
.workflow/WORKFLOW-STATE.txt
README.md
CLAUDE.md

# Gate registry + graph rule content + the checked pre-commit/graph projections.
scripts/gates.list
scripts/graph-vocab.sh
scripts/identity.conf
scripts/git-hooks/pre-commit
.workflow/CHECK-GRAPH.html

# One SPEC.md per kit (each kit's canonical contract).
gate-sdk/SPEC.md
lifecycle-kit/SPEC.md
queue-kit/SPEC.md
spec-kit/SPEC.md
delegation-kit/SPEC.md
context-kit/SPEC.md
guard-kit/SPEC.md
